name: Five Nights at Wario's
summary: Five Nights At Wario's is a parody game of Scott Cawthon's success Five Nights at Freddy's. If this is hilarious or scary, well, that's up to you. It's supposed to be scary, haha! The game has been in production for about 2 months, and now, well, Wario and others are hunting an old Fast Food factory...
